            . I was in the parlour with my mistress and fellow apprentice; my mistress said a girl in a brown cloak had stole something. I and my fellow apprentice ran and took the prisoner. She fell upon her knees and beg'd forgiveness; we took the gauze from her, and brought her and that back.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I met a woman with a scarlet cloak, who gave it me and bid me hold it.</p>
